tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  27,46,"Saalihu (yo o his) maakani ɓe: Ko ɗaɓɓanton yaccinaneeɗe lepte ɗen ko adii yurmeende nden? Ko haɗi ɗaɓɓon haforaneede immorde ka Alla bakkatuuji tijjagol nde O Yurminta on."
  27,51,"Tasko -an Nulaaɗo- ko honno wonirnoo battane pewje maɓɓe e hodooje maɓɓe ɗen? Menen Men mulirnoɓe Lepte ɗen immorde ka Amen ɓe halkaa haa sakkitoro maɓɓe on."